com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query

Class PdbStaticSchemaLoader

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.vernalis.pdbconnector2.query.PdbStaticSchemaLoader

  • public class PdbStaticSchemaLoader
extends java.lang.Object
    This class loads the static schema held in the /json-config folder at the plugin root . It should be seen as a temporary fix until using the correct schema call is implemented
    Since:
    1.28.0
    Author:
    S.Roughley knime@vernalis.com
